measures including but not limited to requiring cessation of
infringement, deletion of related content, cessation of distribution,
cessation of service provision, issuance of notices, preservation of
evidence, pursuit of contractual liability, pursuit of tort liability,
claiming damages, and taking other legal measures. You understand and
agree that Team APE:RIP shall be entitled, in accordance with law, to
